Text: Hur fan kan man censurera en porrfilm, dĂĽ kan man ju lika bra skita i o gĂśra en!

Does anyone know the name of the actress in the first scene?  I'm blown away by her performance and was wondering if I could see her in something else.  I tried to figure out her name from the Japanese, You Nakayamari?  Is this right?  Where can I find her?
Found it.  Rio Nakayama.  Unfortunately, I think this is her best work.
